{"tid":1031787,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"太古坊奪命工業意外　地盤工遭兩噸重玻璃壓斃","createTime":"2019-02-22T01:37:25.000Z","updateTime":"2019-02-22T08:15:45.000Z","uid":20933,"like":2,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":12,"replies":[{"pid":"3fa7c8510405b16ef2deee9c16b2b8f576319fc4","tid":1031787,"uid":20933,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-22T01:37:25.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://fs.mingpao.com/ins/20190222/s00001/bbf5f14095cf3df39252a6551ef2034b.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Ffs.mingpao.com%2Fins%2F20190222%2Fs00001%2Fbbf5f14095cf3df39252a6551ef2034b.jpg&h=8541863b&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n鰂魚涌太古坊發生奪命工業意外，凌晨零時10分，一輛運載大批落地玻璃的重型貨車駛入太古坊1座林肯大廈地庫停車場，26歲姓蘇裝修工與59歲姓馬地盤工合力卸下玻璃時，車上一綑20塊、約1.3米乘3米、重約兩噸的玻璃突然墜下，馬走避不及被擊中頭部，當場重創昏迷。<br />\n<br />\n救護員到場，證實馬已當場身亡。警方經初步調查，將案件列作工業意外處理，案件沒有可疑，勞工處目前正跟進調查意外原因。"},{"pid":"f18f3fecad4b818859e65a315161af9c59fa84bf","tid":1031787,"uid":20933,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-22T01:37:37.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://m.mingpao.com/ins/港聞/article/20190222/s00001/1550798642107/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fm.mingpao.com%2Fins%2F%E6%B8%AF%E8%81%9E%2Farticle%2F20190222%2Fs00001%2F1550798642107%2F&d=YG7PnvT15JjBub1A77CHD6jg55e1U6BcW4s1L%2F%2F48L4%3D&h=d8be66bb\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fm.mingpao.com%2Fins%2F%E6%B8%AF%E8%81%9E%2Farticle%2F20190222%2Fs00001%2F1550798642107%2F&h=b7666eb8\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://m.mingpao.com/ins/港聞/article/20190222/s00001/1550798642107/</a>"},{"pid":"466d5a19c7d41f9ce0b7d9d34e04e5790656a178","tid":1031787,"uid":53026,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-22T02:23:33.000Z","msg":"祝願來生不做中國人<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f6b7f21d357fbd833a3907b075172e2803450cea","tid":1031787,"uid":20933,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-22T02:25:31.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets